'''Alliance Recruiting Center''' was a committee seeking and recruiting new members for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]] received an [[e-mail]] from the Recruiting Center inviting him to join the Alliance, due to their small numbers. The Azzameens joined the Alliance soon after but it is not known if that e-mail had a role in his decision.

